	    (The X Strike Force)</a>
	<li><a href="http://people.debian.org/~jgg/">APT 實驗室</a>
	<li><a href="http://qa.debian.org/">質量保證 (Quality Assurance)</a> 小組
	<li><a href="http://cdimage.debian.org/">Debian GNU/Linux CD 光碟影像</a>
	<li><a href="http://www.internatif.org/bortzmeyer/debian/sponsor/">開發人員保薦計劃 (The Sponsorship Program)</a>
	<li>The <a href="http://oink.cc.ntu.edu.tw/~cklin/signing/">key signing
	    coordination page</a>
	<li><a href="http://people.debian.org/~csmall/ipv6/">Debian IPv6 計劃</a>
	<li><a href="debian-jr/">兒童 Debian (Debian Jr.) 計劃</a>
      </ul>
    </card>
</td>
</tr>

